instruction:
Write a function `roomProperties` that takes three parameters: `width`, `height`, `length`.

The function should return an object with properties `width`, `height` and `length` that will be equal to the corresponding arguments.

Examples of running the function are:
```javascript
roomProperties(10, 20, 30); // { width: 10, height: 20, length: 30 }
roomProperties(5, 10, 15); // { width: 5, height: 10, length: 15 }
```

Similar function:
```javascript
function carProperties(model, year, color) {
  return {
    model,
    year,
    color,
  };
}
